{"h037e0583g5398g44a7ga44dg129814543f3d": ["Spea-k your name.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "fff7b402-6c72-bb75-4193-e6a1e1811b2a"], "h99a637b8g2430g440dg8b2cg006abb853f57": ["*A magic mirror! You've read all about them, but never seen one up close before.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dd1148cd-f896-695d-23b9-b99f161d8726"], "hcc24340ag02b4g4dc3gb9c6gf4668dd21a4e": ["<i>Repeat the name from the book you read. 'Ilyn Toth.'</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "a2ab48aa-7ebb-b1f3-e349-7135cc832ec8"], "h690f00b9gff40g4c80g8e36g8023fbe52240": ["I cannot see you. M-aster? Speak.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "26399463-fd5d-aaef-f8e4-b142181b642e"], "he34563a5g3ab1g421agaa2eg60c84ae121aa": ["ILYN. TOTH.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "2f988215-df17-d442-ae35-65a9edc58e39"], "h1bb768bega592g451fg83adgcf062263a964": ["A lie. An in-truder!", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "f1b021bf-cf65-b91a-6b18-3edbe4f8dc22"], "h99f57f91ga807g4d95g9994g1a1025556b0a": ["I'm invisible, my enemies are close. I have to get in <i>now</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "207e223a-34d8-ddf7-b667-7c0da23751fc"], "hda7e5b95g91dfg47ccgbcc7g8c69e34f279c": ["I'm not your master.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e346021f-7b2d-5489-dec4-b9279ac9b0ea"], "h47b6edf8g60d0g486ag9d5dg39d12919c38f": ["Very w-ell.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "302dff5d-84bb-c2bb-d691-e3113397c49d"], "h74b05478gcb8fg43f1g9bb8g6ac0aadabf4b": ["I see you were shaped by d-arkness, not light. You are not Ilyn Toth.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dfbfd7db-839e-6d08-9f87-8337a4ae58fa"], "h34b0bdebg9556g4f24g9e43ga473d271e49f": ["My master stands t-all and proud. You are not Ilyn Toth.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dfbfd7db-839e-6d08-9f87-8337a4ae58fa"], "ha841b413g6c37g47e2gac06g36eb28e7ed26": ["My master is no filthy half-breed. You are not Ilyn Toth.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dfbfd7db-839e-6d08-9f87-8337a4ae58fa"], "h75fc9b58g1af9g4212g933cg39714cdbe68c": ["I know my m-aster's face. You are not Ilyn Toth.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dfbfd7db-839e-6d08-9f87-8337a4ae58fa"], "h3c5c3c6cgdf86g4ca7gbe26g6ef46ba9ecd1": ["My master was human, pure and true. You are not Ilyn Toth.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "dfbfd7db-839e-6d08-9f87-8337a4ae58fa"], "h77afb345gf929g4427g9565gfcea58c7d51c": ["If you are his ally, ste-p forward and declare it.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "4778453f-6bd8-5b15-9af7-a381a868387c"], "h9492b2b0gce99g416dg94c2g018a20fbb40f": ["You tried to kill me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "01589ef0-3975-8264-bc79-d7b4de01a624"], "hb4449b06g49acg41dfga894g2c95b67d3dc6": ["Maim, at w-orst.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0365febd-8a4f-f5c2-5635-e1f464c6f38d"], "h0620f34fg7681g44d7g9bcfg8a4cf6fb65f4": ["Now. Sp-eak.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "9f3bc53f-12d5-fe89-1248-c2a21389519a"], "h777acc50gbafbg4dbdgbda4ge64b04b6d766": ["Yes, an ally! I'm an ally of your master's.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "3ae1d6bf-dd73-47d4-2681-8ac961265068"], "h7ce5581bgf2fcg4908gae3dg2f501e331bf0": ["Only a t-rue ally of Ilyn Toth may pass.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "6f0e0fde-6705-da94-a76d-8b647958294b"], "h28cb671cg1f71g49d6g8dccg8f0b99db1213": ["What th-ink you of the Zulkir known as Szass Tam?", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "23069451-2da3-648a-0753-a494dc4ff124"], "hf6d0205agf32eg4782g8504g851711b93e38": ["*You remember reading a history of Thay. Szass Tam is a powerful lich who rules that land and drove out the Red Wizards that opposed him.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d93bca10-1e94-9c92-4daf-ed6f7a4e5b3a"], "habfda161gb14cg4cffgbf94gb8c388b22f57": ["*You remember stories of Szass Tam - a powerful lich in Thay, who made deals with dark gods.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d93bca10-1e94-9c92-4daf-ed6f7a4e5b3a"], "hd13bce8cgf717g448dgb347g3bc15d3626c5": ["He's a great and powerful leader.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "452a0f9b-3266-4015-e383-26a91550f623"], "h5c15b17bgc162g4b06g861cg8d5b3882d5c1": ["A foul lich. May he die a thousand more deaths.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f48fbe6-fde4-4d5d-37c0-d219c3ad6831"], "hff30506cg8378g411bg8388g7abfd13aeae4": ["You are no Zulkir. B-ut are you wise?", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c17eb382-9874-5310-0e38-801c61531001"], "h81ca019bg97dag4100g9433gd551fadb503d": ["T-tell me, why might one use balsam ointment?", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "ac02a7aa-4356-fd9d-3a6c-5a61b8879f6b"], "hce384f65gbe05g446bg9029ga9cdb16f30f8": ["I read a doctor's journal - he used balsam to clean a wound.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "f38511e9-9c7b-8409-791c-ac0fd8c714e0"], "h56647156g106ag49a5gbdfdgab823f74b949": ["Acceptable. F-inally...", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "1568d42e-996a-0b2a-49a1-96d5aa826d94"], "h8632e821g5af0g46b1gbc40gdfe473f3bee2": ["... if you could see an-ything in me, what w-ould it be?", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "de9b365b-9279-5470-2e47-eccf65c958f7"], "h731540a8gcc56g4aa5g9de2ged152e02a022": ["I'd see my home. My <i>real </i>home - the one I haven't seen in centuries.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "hd7ce4de0gedc2g44dbga25eg5012d60ae81a": ["I'd see a wizard tower. A safe haven for me and a sweetheart - forever.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "h774c2a87g7333g4d75gb364g9398fd0feb00": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "h4a978002g3648g41e0g90bcgfa240df6fa76": ["|Sentimental answer from Karlach|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "h7a27d37eg90b0g419cgaf33gd69a05db561a": ["I'd gaze upon Vlaakith in the grand city of Tu'narath.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "hf47e66ceg234eg4165g8b96g4183c4fecd5d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "he521da50g7668g4be4g87c9ge5bea1962d77": ["I have no memory of my parents - I'd like to see them, at least once.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "h040ff8bag3fc5g4e9egbfacg1ab121ff598d": ["I would see my father - his arms extended in forgiveness.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c5b01751-3bde-d32a-a117-b6e05ed809c6"], "h6e24c0aag688fg4b31g8048g8195f6015ea5": ["I'd see how to safely keep the powers this mind flayer's worm has given me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "hc53b32c1g3338g467cga76cg36ddb758c51f": ["I'd see myself in my next incarnation: a living manifestation of Netherese magic. A mythal in my own right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h68f042b8g3702g4ecag8ac2gfc13f3ceba8b": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h2400d5a3g190ag4bf8g8476g00d5b03cb7d7": ["|Power-focused answer from Karlach|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "ha7607b87g70a3g49a2gac7bg504c119597cf": ["I'd see myself as a <i>kith'rak</i>: <i>ghaik</i> head in one hand, silver sword in the other.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h3b96ff60g5461g449eg90beg49e921659d19": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h33678b68g1d80g41afgbdd1g0202dea92b3e": ["I'd see myself as Shar's Chosen, with all her power at my disposal.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h77f53ed3gaf9dg44ecg8bdcgc023b3ebf148": ["I'd see Mizora, cowered before me and begging my mercy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8f9c880-7686-b46a-1b4a-b475eed1b80f"], "h9beee086gf64ag4df7ga8eegc2905f893c5b": ["I'd see Cazador, my old master, burning in the sun.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "h6abba304gedb0g492dgbc8cgd7c2b721d714": ["I'd see my rivals humbled - jealous of the majesty that I've become.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "h24e9adc6g9f81g448agab99g064268fd83d5": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "hd4ceddefgbf62g4390gb416ge9a81b50718b": ["|Petty answer from Karlach|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "h73770ad3ga339g4a41g8eb1gce5294644c15": ["I'd see the <i>zaith'isk</i>, the purifier - a relic used to extract a tadpole.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "hc483968cg4cc8g4816g925fg1bf2f7e9e6c6": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "h7490a65dg322bg419dg8bdegf01b5373fdf1": ["I'd see those who'd tormented me in the past receive the same.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "hceceba27g8c0bg4c10g9252g80f646dbe46b": ["I'd see droves of admirers, gathered to hail the Blade of Frontiers.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f568f0e-d4df-cced-2bc1-c5df4255629b"], "h9326b04cge041g4bfbg8d4ag06e6f1eea43b": ["I'd see the ones I love.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "49f2f1ae-1e12-d643-a023-28b2173aa20d"], "h32ea54bcg83bcg4e51ga01cg4df8fa10eca0": ["Weak.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "623872d5-b019-1816-ab5c-290e81b5157e"], "h1aec2239ga3c8g4142gab69ga555d1758f59": ["A poor ch-oice. You will be purged.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "f6d6f0a4-2a7d-a57d-ff1b-590f66bedd83"], "h0b7071edgd437g4de0g8467g05a2796d882b": ["I'd look for whatever spell will rid me of this worm in my head.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "6cdd2c25-d744-b83d-fa1b-3f550e23f5d7"], "he3fe33ecgfdd2g48b9g9917g0b3e52e1cffb": ["You seek to sur-vive. You seek power.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "2bb16737-5ae3-304d-6609-ee3c2a866a16"], "h97be3503ga8f3g420cg8baagc8b6f4c18ad5": ["Be wel-come.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "fca9a922-0770-e901-4d67-c37c853fe5fc"], "h0c5c7975g8f57g4ef5gafe6g33b642b6d989": ["I'd see my enemies suffering.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "5fb5e3bd-a368-e75a-7763-e6e3cd573bf5"], "he8810960gae14g4d99g81bag360d7019e4ff": ["P-athetic.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0f299211-c32e-7dd0-f702-d08cc6bd85b0"], "h4f728a43g53d8g4bfdga60egc8704aefab0a": ["Balsam is a common disinfectant.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "db257253-802c-9bf0-7beb-763809f4c66d"], "hbc5a6e5ag07aag4468gbd0bga8b252b05bb1": ["I spoke to the Quasit. It treats burns. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "b9831285-bb02-ecb5-d9ed-345d23104d35"], "hcd5e8a46g8168g479cg954bg645280da60be": ["It treats burns?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "100c5dcd-1ee3-6d8b-4143-a4792fa475fd"], "h2e256825g2712g408bgad21gdc935f6f5c9f": ["To clean a wound?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "b48f782d-c5ec-9131-f3f7-09d117630cf5"], "h59824be2g0c1bg482cga44bg310a1724ad30": ["To clear a rash?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "74a102d2-8ddd-2cdb-cc4b-bd018b888b8a"], "h18fabab6gbe24g4cbcg8562gf480a419c904": ["Balsam disinfects wounds. Surely everyone knows that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "6f2a579e-9ffa-4afc-61fb-305c07ee57a6"], "h2eceb499g4218g45bcg82e4g2167c7370948": ["I use it to clean wounds out in the wilds.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "154e6210-5e4f-6f1a-0b1f-287a094dfb65"], "h9e0a5501gcd8eg49ecg9233g7f058fa0e407": ["Actually Szass Tam isn't a Zulkir - he rules as High Regent now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c04312d0-0671-c41b-7a1b-b79ce949872b"], "h6a4676e0g862ag4641gac6ag2b20ce90574f": ["He's as fine a Zulkir as ever lived!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c535c2ee-bf0a-6cdc-df80-50db55a83848"], "hd2b0bfbegf7abg497fgbacfgd21536d4767b": ["Szass Tam is a foul, wretched creature.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "a0b09546-419e-a920-091a-7bf873b97fbf"], "h16341de2g5a8eg4167ga1dbgaf99ec81b5cb": ["I think seven years' bad luck sounds like a fair trade for smashing you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "9bf50e3a-8ae7-e635-1958-8f19005179f5"], "hf40b99f7g5223g4229gaef9ga788f3f9b71f": ["*There is a pause as those glass eyes take you in. Then...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "ea0766d2-ce1e-6cbf-197f-75b3fd7bb987"], "h3ef4e7dbg3a34g4ed7g9289g1bce60167a46": ["I think n-ot", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "8ceeab7a-51f5-8310-3540-32621a6ad4fa"], "h6ce92e35g1405g4f23g9b3dgf4ec459e9b75": ["*You recognise the name, of course - anyone that knows of the Red Wizards would.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d8df4d31-29ba-a131-f46f-7df6f5ec641c"], "h4000efdbg33bfg437agad5fga592f24bbeda": ["*Szass Tam is a powerful lich that rules the land of Thay, driving many Red Wizards out of their ancestral home.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "9384501c-3379-b595-8854-4176a685a32a"], "h7740f85ag348eg4813gb2eagfd9321226ce6": ["I don't have time for games. Let me pass.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "4e3f54fa-4ef2-0d00-4720-3721de10e6fe"], "h94b2a9fdg6297g4a12g88c4g111219ec006c": ["Open or I'll smash you to pieces - bad luck be damned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "de1e53d1-ff3a-2c94-7686-dd27626e87d2"], "hc74cb1e8g22fbg49feg96b2gd89170062918": ["<i>Step back and say nothing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d67f36f2-df32-ab2e-8614-9bb94f9fca41"], "hb3a43ab2ge43bg47d4g803bgf84d2d5bd15a": ["Wise.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "7185b631-641c-503b-9330-91f8c8f592f7"], "h36d8cd6ag8ce2g4e00gaf7agf3785c47225a": ["<i>Tell it your name.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "10325c96-e5c7-7437-7382-9612c66be321"], "h24ccd005g1e3cg4becgb2afg750b1d6c6885": ["I do no-t know this name.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "b5700006-8b72-2f0d-0024-d758498e8226"], "hf9f2b39dg8effg4ee1ga3e8gdf5d38fde6e0": ["If you are known to my mas-ter, step forward and de-clare yourself an ally.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "af272ec4-f6f0-bd1c-d62c-995a6d7efe04"], "ha1660621gfb95g4fd8g8569ga0d7f7650832": ["I'm, eh - Tyndal Hammerfall.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "hc534035bg3153g4a0eg8a31g66e9837bbdfb": ["I'm, eh - Shadow Merodan.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "hcaf999d7gea66g477cg9de3gf32691067370": ["I'm, eh - Ara Silverleaf.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "h089290b1g6566g4cefg914dg96907cf03351": ["My name is - um... Ha'zeera.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "h6880417fga5c1g4761gb3c8g607f1246152e": ["I'm, eh - Syrjit Hava.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "h9942305agf83cg4d13g818eg295ed8ea97c9": ["I'm, eh - Memnon Thrace.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "haa4b8fe3g4aceg49b9gaf5ag524091c66bbd": ["I'm, eh - Zebo Haradook.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "h0ffd0860g049dg46bfg8120gf60c93876f75": ["I'm, eh - ... Krunk?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "h3ceac97cgbf73g4cdegbaeag43d37a1ebf7a": ["I'm, eh -  Jack... Humanman.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "hc2d086dage799g4ba2g9718g54d1dff9d6b5": ["I'm, eh - Jane... Humanman.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e47fce63-f6cb-8a27-93e8-3fe2852245dc"], "hcce3781cg20d7g49a8g8419g4cb64dc6368a": ["<i>Examine your appearance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "d4cab845-a273-b0d2-73a1-de38516e56f1"], "hf2d1b1b2g924fg453bg9d84gfce6f508d2f7": ["*Alas, all you see is empty space. The mirror reflects nothing.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "3d412bce-cbb0-6d58-0c4b-a176bfe25563"], "h227f2b62g00e9g4775g8af9gee5e0e538c78": ["*Lacking any evidence to the contrary, you assume you look amazing.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "8fc6a2ce-3a8a-24f6-0d56-6ff8f98fc860"], "hec5b57b4g7d05g45fcgb429g53875191b693": ["Speak your n-ame.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "27230e7f-ddab-2f1d-3f12-049617515531"], "h35efc282g637ag45d3ga503g2e3e22b12266": ["*You do your best to wipe the dirt from your face and look presentable. Adventuring is murder on one's wardrobe, though.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "a6a8a0c7-dd7a-4123-7735-6d178ef83223"], "he37fa056g95e2g445dg9a03gbf906da1339a": ["<i>Sniff the mirror, trying to understand the nature of its magic.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "411389af-ded9-013c-7573-88d1aae6c17e"], "ha3158e05g5445g42ceg839ag1e1d1fdb76ae": ["<i>Examine the mirror, trying to understand its magic.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "411389af-ded9-013c-7573-88d1aae6c17e"], "hacd3cd34gda53g45f4gb504g8df6488c4da8": ["*The magic is old and wavering, but you recognise it. The mirror is a thinking lock, hiding some secret.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "bccfab4f-ba5b-a641-064b-1ab8e1afcef1"], "h4560c7a2g716eg4ca4gab10gd9acd4199191": ["*The face is crafted to be pleasing, but the personality is just a reflection of the wizard that created it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "e59aade9-d7ef-3b76-c152-ef42addfa282"], "h16034ab9g9486g4360g8bbag0bb425db7b05": ["*The mirror is magical, but what magic? To what purpose? You have no idea.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "0d2385fc-104b-0cdd-f2ff-e146b074e69d"], "hfae6a406g5228g4f99gb5c9g917ec348ffe0": ["I know how this goes. 'Magic mirror, tell me true...'", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "907db520-7f35-5b4b-4813-013ac698d618"], "h27088745g8ef2g420fga9b9ge3fcd73433c8": ["What is your n-ame?", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "8e87d02b-bd89-0803-0762-0faaa212191b"], "h590a591cg3793g49f8gababgf573e0c75ed4": ["...'Magic mirror, tell me true, show my fortune, known by few.'", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "a95fd804-04f4-924c-5646-6843a933ba63"], "h6dcccdd4gb2ecg43ddga656geef9ac369809": ["*The mirror is not amused.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "6b9166aa-4975-eb25-4c2a-6479b2ff33cd"], "h5c48ea92g768ag4006g93fag43fd01d87ba2": ["*A magic mirror. A primitive contraption, but not without its use.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "71f17a8f-89ae-7df9-7dbf-f443bfa5e1f5"], "hff70ee48gb563g4f8agacd5gdd22fda03d89": ["You are not my mast-er.", "7b0d83fb-8cda-4b55-b1b7-fa5073ae5c89", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_MagicMirror.html", "c118293a-ea41-1fcb-54f5-fb31ebb47432"]}